main - package main
 
MAIN - Class in main
Starts the program and loads the scenes and user preferences and high scores for the game;
MAIN() - Constructor for class main.MAIN
The constructor that sets the instance field to reference this; THIS SHOULD ACTUALLY NEVER BE USED.
main(String[]) - Static method in class main.MAIN
This is just a fail-safe in case the start method does not work; The documentation on JavaFX has more info about this.
mainMenuScene - Static variable in class main.MAIN
Stores the menu scene for easy reference;
MainMenuUIController - Class in main
This class controls all of the UI elements displayed while in the main menu scene.

mainStage - Static variable in class main.MAIN
